lead_paragraph: In an application for a search warrant from October, unsealed by a judge on Tuesday, the F.B.I. said that there was probable cause to believe that Huma Abedin’s emails contained classified information because she had communicated with Hillary Clinton so frequently.

headline.main: Search Warrant Application for Huma Abedin’s Emails
